* Libraries from Repositories
** PyPI (Python)
***_ Enter package name
***_ Pin exact version for production
***_ e.g. pymssql==2.3.9
** Maven (Java/Scala)
***_ Format: groupId:artifactId:version
***_ e.g. com.microsoft.sqlserver:mssql-jdbc:13.2.1.jre11
***_ Can exclude transitive dependencies
** CRAN (R)
***_ Always installs latest version
***_ Pin versions via files instead
** Standard access mode
***_ Maven/JAR requires allowlist approval
***_ Security control on shared compute
@endmindmap
